Package: BJM
Title: Backward Joint Model for Joint Dynamic Prediction of Survival and Multivariate Longitudinal Outcomes with or without Competing Risk Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Wenhao", "li", email = "liwh0904@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5050-443X"))
           )
Maintainer: Wenhao Li <liwh0904@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides tools for fitting joint models that integrate multivariate longitudinal and time-to-event data for dynamic prediction. It enables joint dynamic prediction of survival and future longitudinal outcomes, with or without competing risks. The implementation accommodates multiple biomarkers measured at irregular time points and is designed for prediction-focused analyses rather than parameter interpretation.
